lead_paragraph: PARIS  Moscow signed several deals in autos and energy with French companies on Friday at a meeting described by Prime Minister Vladimir V. Putin of Russia as a breakthrough in economic ties between the countries.

headline.main: Russia and France Reach Agreements on Autos and Natural Gas Pipelines
